{"tha-ap224:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap224:0.2":"Alambanadayakavagga ","tha-ap224:0.3":"Ajinadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap224:1.1":"“Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap224:1.2":"ganasattharako aham; ","tha-ap224:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap224:1.4":"ahutinam patiggaham. ","tha-ap224:2.1":"Cammakhandam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap224:2.2":"sikhino lokabandhuno; ","tha-ap224:2.3":"Tena kammena dvipadinda, ","tha-ap224:2.4":"lokajettha narasabha. ","tha-ap224:3.1":"Sampattim anubhotvana, ","tha-ap224:3.2":"kilese jhapayim aham; ","tha-ap224:3.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap224:3.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap224:4.1":"Ekattimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap224:4.2":"ajinam yam adasaham; ","tha-ap224:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap224:4.4":"ajinassa idam phalam. ","tha-ap224:5.1":"Ito pancamake kappe, ","tha-ap224:5.2":"raja asim sudayako; ","tha-ap224:5.3":"Sattaratanasampanno, ","tha-ap224:5.4":"cakkavatti mahabbalo. ","tha-ap224:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap224:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap224:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap224:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ajinadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap224:8.1":"Ajinadayakattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}